  "body": "It'd be nice to have the following API:\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nclass ComponentA extends PureComponent {\r\n  shouldComponentUpdate(newProps, newState) {\r\n   if (this.props.anyProp.nestedObject !== newProps.anyProp.nestedObject) {\r\n      return true\r\n    }\r\n    return super.shouldComponentUpdate(newProps, newState) // from pureComponent\r\n  }\r\n  render() {\r\n     return <ComponentB propToB={this.props.anyProp} />\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n",
